# Cached artifacts produced by the eval pipeline.
# These regenerate from proforma.pdf + the live Brave/Gemini/Claude APIs
# whenever they're missing — committing them would create churn and bloat.
#
# Keep checked in:
#   - source files (test_*.py, conftest.py, judge.py, judge_cache.py, ...)
#   - fixture inputs (proforma.pdf, metadata.json)
#   - documentation (TEST_PLAN.md, README.md, results.md)
#
# Ignore the derived caches and reports:

# Per-fixture caches
fixtures/*/web_context.txt
fixtures/*/pis_data*.json
fixtures/*/judge_*_cache.json

adversarial/*/web_context.txt
adversarial/*/pis_data*.json
adversarial/*/judge_*_cache.json

# Timestamped run reports
runs/*.json

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc
